  "design_notes": "The chart is designed for a casual-first experience, focusing on a clean 1-beat rhythm. In the intro, we establish a spacious 2-beat cadence alternating lanes to let players get used to the highway. During the high-energy drop, the density increases smoothly to a 1-beat flow pattern, utilizing a looping swept rotation (BAR-GAP-NOTE) to keep hands moving naturally without double-tapping. The outro mirrors the intro's spacing for a relaxing wind-down.",
